Box 68, 108 West Stuart Drive, Galax, VA 24333 Office Hours are 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, 33767=Copyright © 2015 The Galax Gazette is your source for local news, sports, events and information in Galax, Grayson, Carroll, and surrounding areas., 19899=HILLSVILLE — Long-time Hillsville town manager Larry South has taken a job in a place he knows well from his youth. North Wilkesboro, N.C., hired South to fill a town manager vacancy there last week, after his almost 19 years of service in Hillsville. He resigned from the post in June. A native of Ashe County, N.C., South notes that he watched many a race and bowled in North Wilkesboro while growing up.}
